<% content_for :title, "Copyright Claims - YouTube to MP3 Converter" %>
<% content_for :description, "Information about how to submit copyright claims related to content converted through our YouTube to MP3 service." %>

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Copyright Claims</h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
      We respect intellectual property rights and are committed to following all applicable copyright laws. This page outlines our policy regarding copyright claims.
    </p>
    
    <div class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">DMCA Compliance</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        YT Converter operates in compliance with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA). If you believe that your copyrighted work has been used in a way that constitutes copyright infringement, please provide us with the following information:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>A physical or electronic signature of the copyright owner or a person authorized to act on their behalf</li>
        <li>Identification of the copyrighted work claimed to have been infringed</li>
        <li>Identification of the material that is claimed to be infringing and information reasonably sufficient to permit us to locate the material</li>
        <li>Your contact information, including your address, telephone number, and email</li>
        <li>A statement that you have a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained of is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law</li>
        <li>A statement that the information in the notification is accurate, and under penalty of perjury, that you are authorized to act on behalf of the copyright owner</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How to Submit a Claim</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-1">
        Copyright claims should be submitted to our designated copyright agent at:
        <a href="mailto:copyright@youtubetomp3converter.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">copyright@youtubetomp3converter.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Our Response</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-1">
        Upon receiving a valid copyright claim, we will promptly remove or disable access to the allegedly infringing material and notify the user who posted it. Users who believe their content was removed in error may submit a counter-notification.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>